<db:section xml:id="initialize-method">
<db:title>void initialize(WaylandCompositor <db:emphasis>compositor</db:emphasis>, WaylandClient <db:emphasis>client</db:emphasis>, int <db:emphasis>id</db:emphasis>, int <db:emphasis>version</db:emphasis>)</db:title>
<db:para>Initializes the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtwayland-compositor-waylandsurface.xml">WaylandSurface</db:link> with the given <db:code role="parameter">compositor</db:code> and <db:code role="parameter">client</db:code>, and with the given <db:code role="parameter">id</db:code> and <db:code role="parameter">version</db:code>.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="isDestroyed-method">
<db:title>bool isDestroyed()</db:title>
<db:para>Returns <db:code>true</db:code> if the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtwayland-compositor-waylandsurface.xml">WaylandSurface</db:link> has been destroyed. Otherwise returns <db:code>false</db:code>.</db:para>
</db:section>
